verbs.description: The S&P 500 [V: has] been stuck in neutral since mid - May , squeezed between a rocket - propelled U.S. economy and fears over the stability of the European Union and a Trump trade war . One chart watcher says this stock market is still a good place for bulls despite the geopolitical risk .
